  "Description": {
    "English": "The shattered remnants of a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">previous existence</span>. It whispers, an unknowable name deep within its fibres.<br><br>The memory will manifest as a <span class=\"name name-technology\">starship weapon</span> to aid you in this iteration. <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Absorb</span> this memory with <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><>.<br><br><span class=\"name name-special\">DEATH IS NOT THE END</span> <span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span> <span class=\"name name-stellar\">THE LOOP CONTINUES</span>",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一块 <span class=\"name name-stellar\">已故生命体</span>的记忆碎片残骸。在纤维的深处仿佛轻轻的低语着一个陌生的名字。<br><br>这些记忆将作为一个<span class=\"name name-technology\">飞船武器组件</span>来帮助你进行此次迭代。按<span class=\"name name-stellar\"><>FE_ALT1<VAL_ON><IMG></span>吸收<>这份记忆。<br><br><span class=\"name name-special\">死亡不是结束</span><span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">循环将会继续</span>",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-stellar\">前世存在</span>的破碎殘片。不斷發出低語，其纖維中深藏著一個不可知的名字。<br><br>記憶將會以<span class=\"name name-technology\">太空船武器</span>的形式顯現，在這一個迭代中協助你。按下 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> <span class=\"name name-stellar\">吸收</span>這個記憶。<br><br><span class=\"name name-special\">死亡並非終結</span> <span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span> <span class=\"name name-stellar\">迴圈將會繼續</span>"
  },
